OL,6,FIan Powell, who's 60 and worked as a
OL,7,Ftutor at Coleg Gwent, admitted the
OL,8,Foffences involving a teenage girl.
OL,10,FNewport Crown Court heard that the
OL,11,Fgirl, who can't be named for legal
