OL,3,CTutor given suspended sentence after
OL,4,Cmaking indecent images of a child
OL,6,FThe court was told that there had been
OL,7,Fsome hugging and kissing - described
OL,8,Fas 'snogging' - between the two in a
OL,9,Flocal park. Powell went on to buy the
OL,10,Fteenager sex toys.
OL,12,FThe messaging between the pair later
OL,13,Fbecame sexual, with the girl sending a
OL,14,Fnumber of indecent images to the
OL,15,Fdefendant.
OL,17,F7 of these - including 2 videos - were
OL,18,Fin Category A, the most serious
OL,19,Fcategory. 8 images were in Category B
OL,20,Fand 32 in Category C, the least
OL,21,Fserious.
