OL,3,CTutor given suspended sentence after
OL,4,Cmaking indecent images of a child
OL,6,FSentencing, Judge Shomon Khan said he
OL,7,Faccepted that the defendant had shown
OL,8,F"genuine remorse", but that "nothing
OL,9,Fcould explain" what Powell had done.
OL,11,F"You were grooming (the victim).
OL,12,FThere's no other conclusion that I can
OL,13,Fdraw."
OL,15,F"Your career is destroyed. You deserve
OL,16,Fthat for putting your own sexual needs
OL,17,Fbefore the victim's welfare."
OL,19,FIan Powell was sentenced to 10 months
OL,20,Fin prison suspended for 2 years.
